'''Mary Elizabeth Dawson''' (9 May 1833&ndash;22 February 1924) was a New Zealand servant, farmer, environmentalist and nurse. She was born in [[Mersham]], [[Kent]], [[England]] on 9 May 1833.<ref name="DNZB Dawson">{{DNZB|title=Mary Elizabeth Dawson|first= Patricia A.|last= Sargison|id=1d5|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

